evaluateCell

private Object evaluateCell(int rowNum,
                            int column,
                            String cellVal,
                            String authString)
Determines whether a single cell of the response table contains the indicated value.

Parameters:
rowNum - the 1-based row number being examined; for debugging and verification failure only
column - the 1-based column number being examined; for debugging and verification failure only
cellVal - a single cell of the table
authString - string to which to compare the response
Returns:
0 (nonmatch) or 1 (match) if no verification failure has been found; otherwise, String describing the failure
